# --- Unity tekstowe (NIE w LFS) ---
*.unity          text
*.prefab         text
*.variant        text
*.overrideController text
*.controller     text
*.anim           text
*.asset          text
*.mat            text
*.mask           text
*.physicMaterial text
*.terrainlayer   text
